    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((tmp / (v0 + 0.76 + v1 + 0.19)) + wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.84)))
    v1 = wp.abs(0.42)
    v2 = (wp.sin(tmp) + tmp)
    tmp = (((v0 + 0.09 + v2 + 0.05) + 0.56) * wp.cos(0.86))
    v2 = wp.cos(v0)
    tmp = 0.69
    v0 = ((0.95 / (v1 + 1.00 + v1 + 0.82)) * (wp.exp(v1 + 0.99) + wp.sin(v1 + 0.70)))
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
